lead_paragraph: Thousands of fans stood and applauded in a moving 14th-minute tribute to Johan Cruyff during the friendly between England and the Netherlands at Wembley on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Thousands Pay Tribute to Cruyff in 14th Minute at Wembley
